                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="summary-box">
                        <span class="icon"><span class="fa fa-desktop"></span></span>
                        <h1>WEBSITE DESIGN</h1>
                        <p>We create beautifully designed websites that your audience can engage with.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
